		<title>A Saint, A disciple, or both?</title>
		<link>http://www.brianbowen.com/?p=266</link>
		<comments>http://www.brianbowen.com/?p=266#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 30 Sep 2008 13:07:28 +0000</pubDate>
